msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "That's too bad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "After all that, we still don't know\r\nwhy exactly Tatsukawa was killed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "You risked your necks busting into\r\nLittle Asia, and still came up empty."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Well, we know that Tatsukawa betraying\r\nthe triads had something to do with it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "It's also possible Haruka's accident\r\nwas related to that betrayal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "And the Saio Triad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Would they really try to kill Haruka and\r\nher year-old son just to send a message?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "I wouldn't put it past them. Either way,\r\nwe need to keep Haruto out of Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Date-san, it was a good call moving\r\nHaruka to the police hospital, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "That aside, there's still a lot that's\r\nunclear about Tatsukawa's situation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "We need answers.\r\nThat's why I'm going to meet Lo tonight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "But with Tatsukawa and Masuzoe, we know\r\nthe triads have already infiltrated Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Why exactly would they do that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Even you're stumped, Date-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "I'm speechless about all this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "It's hard to believe there were really\r\ntriads livin' among us this whole time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "I mean, Tatsukawa n' I have been\r\nfriends since we were kids."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "I dunno who to trust anymore..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "And what could that secret of Onomichi\r\nthat Lo mentioned be?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Who knows. All I care about is why\r\nthe Saio decided to kill Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "If it doesn't involve Haruka, they can\r\nkeep their secrets to themselves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "You... Someya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "This bastard?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Hey, no fighting in here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Wasn't expectin' t'see yer sorry ass\r\nafter comin' all the way up t'Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Whaddya want, huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Ha. What do you think of\r\nthe ladies in Kamurocho?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "They must be night and day from\r\nthe country folk, Nagumo-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "I heard you had a good time\r\nwhile Kiryu-san was at that host club."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "H-How d'ya even know that!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Every inch of this city belongs\r\nto the Tojo Clan. Did you forget?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "If you'd like, I can reveal not only\r\nwhere you went, but what you did."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Yer a right puckered asshole!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "What do you want, Someya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "I half expect your men at every corner,\r\nbut I wasn't expecting a personal call."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "I have a request, Fourth Chairman.\r\nNothing too egregious, don't worry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "I'll get to the point, Fourth Chairman.\r\nHow would you feel about an alliance?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "What the hell?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "You met with Lo from the Saio Triad\r\nlast night, did you not?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Some of my men said they saw\r\nhim going into Little Asia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Interestingly enough, those same men\r\nsaid they saw you there as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "And?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Any chance you'll meet him again?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "If indeed you are, I'd like to\r\naccompany you to such a meeting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "What are you planning?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "As you're well aware, the Tojo Clan is\r\nensnared in a brutal war with Lo's triad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Neither side seems satisfied with the\r\nbloodshed, and there's no end in sight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "I'd hoped to strike a deal with Lo,\r\nbut he's been quite secretive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "That is, ever since that\r\nincident occurred."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "What incident?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Didn't you hear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "His son, Jimmy Lo,\r\nwas murdered in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Jimmy was a Saio officer in charge of\r\norganizing their forces in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "He stood to inherit the triad, but instead\r\nhe wound up full of maggots in some dark alley."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "So, did the Tojo Clan kill Lo's son?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "I'd rather not answer that in front\r\nof our detective friend here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Consider this conversation off the record.\r\nNot like we could pursue it without evidence."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "In that case, I have no idea\r\nwho killed Jimmy Lo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "His father seems quite certain\r\nthe Tojo Clan were behind it, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Hence, meeting with him is imperative\r\nto ending this war between us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Please bring me to Lo, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "It's only fair that you help the Tojo Clan\r\nevery so often, wouldn't you say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Pipe down. Aniki don't gotta\r\nlisten t'ya if he doesn't wanna."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "N' besides, Aniki's got some real important\r\nstuff o' his own t'talk to Lo about!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "So you <font_kind=yakuza_italic>are</font_kind> going to see him again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Someya. I need one answer first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "There's this rumor I heard..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "...That the fire in Little Asia that invited\r\nthe Saio Triad in was set by the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Is that one you've heard before?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "I certainly have."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "According to the rumor, Sugai-san and I\r\nactually orchestrated the whole thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "And after you brought the Saio Triad into\r\nKamurocho, you staged a war with them..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "...Leading the police to arrest the sixth\r\nchairman on related charges."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "With him in the picture, you and Sugai\r\ncould never control the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "But now, the fake conflict you started with\r\nthe Saio Triad has turned into a very real war."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "That's what the rumors say, anyway."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "If that rumor were true..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "...That would make Sugai-san and myself\r\nlittle more than traitors to the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "It's preposterous."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "I've answered your question,\r\nFourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "And? What will you do?\r\nAre you going to help me or not?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Fine. Come back here later tonight\r\nand I'll bring you with me to see Lo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "A-Aniki! Y'sure 'bout this!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "But you should know, Lo is expecting\r\nme to come alone tonight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "I couldn't tell you how he'll respond\r\nwhen he sees a yakuza by my side."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "I'll take that risk.\r\nThank you for this, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "Aniki, y'can't do that! That freakin' bastard\r\nSomeya jus' wants t'kill Lo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "N' if he actually does it, how're we gonna\r\nget our answers 'bout Tatsukawa!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "It'll be okay. I know he wants to kill Lo,\r\nbut I'll be there if he tries."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "If I'd turned Someya down, who knows\r\nwhat violence he'd resort to?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "If he's going to act like a feral dog,\r\nit's better that I'm holding the leash."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "Nice. That's classic Sun Tzu:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "\"Keep your friends close,\r\nand your enemies closer.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "Hot damn.\r\nThat's actually kinda cool."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Someya's coming back\r\nhere to meet up with you tonight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Once you take him to Lo, there's\r\nno telling what might happen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Make sure you're ready for\r\nanything to go down, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "Yeah, good point."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "We'll wait here fer ya, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "Ain't heard a peep from Tagashira n' Matsunaga\r\nin Hiroshima, so I'll ring 'em up n' get the skinny."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "(Things might get messy tonight. I should\r\nstock up if I need to before Someya gets here...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Are you ready for tonight?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "If so, you might wanna relax until then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Yeah, that sounds good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Okay. I'll let you know\r\nwhen Someya gets here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "No, there are still some things\r\nI need to do first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Okay. Just let me know when\r\nyou're ready, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "Isn't this the same scene I left?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "Someya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "As promised, I'm back.\r\nHaving second thoughts, Fourth Chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "No, you don't need to worry.\r\nI'll bring you to Lo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "Aniki. If this prissy boy tries anythin',\r\nwe'll be there t'back ya up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "Call us if y'need us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "Hell, I'd be happy t'sock 'im."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "Where exactly are we meeting\r\nLo, Fourth Chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "He said he would wait for us in\r\nan old brothel called Shangri-La."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "Shangri-La?\r\nWhat's he doing there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Something wrong with that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "Well, you'll see when we get there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "Aniki. Y'better not let yer guard down\r\n'round Someya. He's dangerous."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki. Be careful out there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "Make sure you come home safe, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "So, what did Lo say to get you to meet\r\nwith him again, Fourth Chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "It has nothing to do with the Tojo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "I'd rather not tell you anything\r\nmore than I have to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "I do wish you could relax a little."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "Anyway, I wouldn't expect the warmest\r\nwelcome from Lo over in Shangri-La."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "Why do you say that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "It's not quite what it used to be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "Nobody has set foot in there\r\nsince the brothel closed down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "All you're going to find there are\r\nthe dregs of society."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "To venture a guess, I think Lo has every\r\nintention of testing you, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "He probably wants to see if forming an\r\nalliance with you is really a viable option."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "What are you doing, Fourth Chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "Where exactly are you going?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "We should probably avoid detours."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "Shangri-La is this way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "There's really no need to run."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "Remember to pace yourself,\r\nFourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "Patience is not your strong suit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "Hold on a moment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "It looks like those guys want a fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "How about some exercise?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "We should ignore these weaklings."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "Seems they don't know their place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "Let's mop this up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "You don't stand a chance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Here we are. Shangri-La."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "Lo has probably already noticed that\r\nI've come with you, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "Let's hope he still wants to talk,\r\nnow that you've broken your word."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "I hope so. This would be\r\na complete waste of time if not."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "Well, I suppose we'll learn\r\nthe truth once we're inside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "I'm shocked he asked to meet you here, though.\r\nLo clearly doesn't know how to treat his guests."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "Yeah, for once I agree with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "It's been ten years, hasn't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "After Third Chairman Sera died, part of\r\nthe war for the Tojo Clan took place here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "You remember, of course?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "The Dragon of Dojima and the Mad Dog\r\nof Shimano clashed here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "Apparently, he drove a dump\r\ntruck right through the wall."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "It's your fault this place\r\nis in this state, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "Your toxic legacy left its mark\r\nacross this entire city, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "These days, the places that couldn't\r\nbounce back are gang strongholds."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "I've heard what they do\r\nto innocent women, too..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "The police are too busy with the\r\nwar to do anything, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "Their inability to act has created\r\nlawless zones throughout the city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "Well? Do you feel even a shred of\r\nresponsibility, Fourth Chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "Either way, if Lo really is in this building..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "...Wouldn't you think it likely that\r\nour friends here are on his payroll?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "You're saying Lo sent a welcoming party?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "They don't appear to be in\r\na very welcoming mood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "I doubt those weapons are\r\nmeant for conversation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "Come on, we can't afford to waste time\r\nwith these punks. Let's go, Fourth Chairman!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "No chance we're getting up those stairs.\r\nLet's find another route."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "There's a passage behind this rubble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "We should be able to get through\r\nif we can clear it somehow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "Let's clear this rubble.\r\nYou take that side."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "A good kick from the both of us\r\nshould work, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "Are you ready, Fourth Chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "Come on. Ready, go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196||||4"
msgid "One, two, three!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "Nice, that should do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "I think we could break through\r\nthe lock if we tried."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman.\r\nUse this to break the lock."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "Nicely done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "Hm? Who is that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "Hm? What do we have here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "Quite the spectacle, no?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman. Let's just\r\nleave him be and move on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "This place is an absolute mess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "There's no time to waste.\r\nLet's keep moving."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "207||||4"
msgid "It's sad to see it like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "208||||4"
msgid "The finest brothel in Kamurocho,\r\nreduced to rubble and debris."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "209||||4"
msgid "Time hasn't been kind to this place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "210||||4"
msgid "Let's try going up that ladder."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "211||||4"
msgid "A dead end."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212||||4"
msgid "Another dead end..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "213||||4"
msgid "Let's find another way through."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "214||||4"
msgid "Hm? This wall looks pretty cracked."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "215||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman. The walls have deteriorated\r\nin a few places. They seem quite weak."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216||||4"
msgid "If only we had a tool to smash\r\nthrough this part of the wall."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "217||||4"
msgid "This wall looks weak."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "218||||4"
msgid "Maybe we should find something\r\nto break it with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "219||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman! You might want\r\nto take a look over there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "220||||4"
msgid "That's actually a pretty nice find."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "221||||4"
msgid "Give that hammer a nice swing\r\nat that wall we encountered earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "223||||4"
msgid "Incredible!\r\nWe can continue onward now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224||||4"
msgid "It seems there are other breakable\r\nwalls in here, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "225||||4"
msgid "(I should be able to break this wall, too.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "226||||4"
msgid "(If only I had a hammer...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "227||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman. This floor is slippery,\r\nso watch your step."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228||||4"
msgid "Try to keep your balance!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "229||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "230||||4"
msgid "Hey, Fourth Chairman!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "231||||4"
msgid "Hello? Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "232||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman! You still alive?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "233||||4"
msgid "I think there's something over there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "236||||4"
msgid "What is this guy!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "238||||4"
msgid "So strong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "239||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman! Can you hear me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "240||||4"
msgid "I'll wait for you up here.\r\nGet here quick, would you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "241||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'll be right there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "242||||4"
msgid "You took your time, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "243||||4"
msgid "We should be able to jump\r\nover this blockade."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "244||||4"
msgid "The enemy is hiding from us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "245||||4"
msgid "Stay on guard, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "246||||4"
msgid "Come on, let's finish them off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "247||||4"
msgid "Hm? Still more of them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248||||4"
msgid "They really want to fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "249||||4"
msgid "I learn nothing from fighting this trash."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "250||||4"
msgid "The floor is giving way all over here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "251||||4"
msgid "Do try not to fall through."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "252||||4"
msgid "This is bad!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "254||||4"
msgid "Man, that hurts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "255||||4"
msgid "Huh!? Who is this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "256||||4"
msgid "I knew this would happen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "257||||4"
msgid "It seems we'll have to settle things\r\nwith him before we can proceed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "258||||4"
msgid "I'm exhausted."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "259||||4"
msgid "I expect Lo is tired of waiting for us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260||||4"
msgid "We should continue onward."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "261||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. I thought we had agreed\r\nthat you would come alone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "262||||4"
msgid "What is the meaning of his presence here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "263||||4"
msgid "Lo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "264||||4"
msgid "I've come to expect betrayal in this country,\r\nthough. All thanks to Someya-san, that is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "265||||4"
msgid "Long time no see, Lo-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "266||||4"
msgid "It's no wonder our search of Little Asia\r\ncame up empty if this is where you've been."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "267||||4"
msgid "There are still a great many places in\r\nKamurocho outside of Tojo control."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "268||||4"
msgid "This is but one of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "269||||4"
msgid "All too true. However, I would ask that\r\nyou kindly relocate from this place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "270||||4"
msgid "Your stench has become overbearing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "271||||4"
msgid "Don't forget that it was you yakuza\r\nwho invited us into this city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "272||||4"
msgid "You were the ones who killed\r\nmy son as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "273||||4"
msgid "I knew it.\r\nThe rumors were true, Someya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "274||||4"
msgid "You and Lo conspired together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "275||||4"
msgid "First you burned down Little Asia and\r\nbrought the Saio in to rise from the ashes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "276||||4"
msgid "Then you started a fake war\r\nto get the police after Daigo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "277||||4"
msgid "Correct. But as you can see, the war\r\nwith the Chinese is quite real now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "278||||4"
msgid "Once Sugai-san took over the Tojo Clan,\r\nhe felt it necessary to eliminate the Saio."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "279||||4"
msgid "They proved quite resilient, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "280||||4"
msgid "It bears repeating, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "281||||4"
msgid "Join forces with me, please."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "283||||4"
msgid "Until recently, I'd thought killing\r\nLo here was the only option I had."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "284||||4"
msgid "But together, we'd have no\r\ntrouble taking him captive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "286||||4"
msgid "Besides, you would stop me if I actually\r\ntried to kill him now, wouldn't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "287||||4"
msgid "After all, he possesses information\r\nyou very much desire."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "288||||4"
msgid "Think about it, though. If we capture him,\r\nyou can ask anything you want of him later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "289||||4"
msgid "Having Lo in captivity would also help\r\nme suppress the Saio further down the line."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "290||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Can you leave him to me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "291||||4"
msgid "My son was murdered right here\r\nin Kamurocho, after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "293||||4"
msgid "That's all true."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "294||||4"
msgid "You make no excuses?\r\nHowever, the Tojo Clan wasn't responsible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "295||||4"
msgid "The one who killed my son is the puppet\r\nmaster of the Yomei Alliance, Tsuneo Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "296||||4"
msgid "Tsuneo Iwami...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "297||||4"
msgid "The son of Chairman Kurusu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "298||||4"
msgid "The very same. He brought us\r\nhere to use as an instrument..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "299||||4"
msgid "...To change the Tojo Clan's leadership\r\nas he saw fit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "300||||4"
msgid "With this done, he attempted to kill me,\r\nbut it was my son who paid the price."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "301||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "302||||4"
msgid "As for Someya and his patron, Sugai,\r\nthey would be nothing if not for Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "303||||4"
msgid "In other words, they are pawns,\r\nunworthy of bullets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "305||||4"
msgid "I'll make sure you regret\r\nthose words, Lo-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "306||||4"
msgid "You really think it wise to free\r\nthe man who just tried to kill you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "307||||4"
msgid "If I had to kill every man who wished\r\nme dead, I would never sleep again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "308||||4"
msgid "More men have conspired against me\r\nthan there are stars in the sky."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "310||||4"
msgid "It would be simple to kill you here, yes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "311||||4"
msgid "However, that would only serve to prod\r\nthe hornet's nest that is the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "312||||4"
msgid "It would be foolish to incite the hive\r\njust to crush one large bee underfoot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "313||||4"
msgid "That's all I am?\r\nOne bee in a hive?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "314||||4"
msgid "Exactly. Furthermore, you will owe me a\r\ndebt of gratitude if I spare you now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "315||||4"
msgid "Gratitude? And what if I told you\r\nI'm not the gracious type?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "316||||4"
msgid "You can do as you wish."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "317||||4"
msgid "However, leaving you alive only lessens\r\nyour threat to me, not raises it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "319||||4"
msgid "Interesting. I wouldn't have expected a\r\nresponse like this from such a powerful man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "320||||4"
msgid "That said, I want you to\r\ntell Tsuneo Iwami something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "321||||4"
msgid "If it means avenging my son, I am\r\nprepared to risk all. Even my life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "322||||4"
msgid "I'll make sure he knows. Thank you for the\r\nlesson today, Lo-san. And Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "323||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Do you object to how\r\nI chose to deal with him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "324||||4"
msgid "No, not at all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "325||||4"
msgid "Watching you fight him gave me a good\r\nimpression of the kind of man you are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "326||||4"
msgid "That was ultimately all I wanted\r\nout of our meeting today anyway."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "327||||4"
msgid "Unfortunately, I didn't come all this\r\nway to learn more about you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "328||||4"
msgid "I need to know about Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "329||||4"
msgid "That's the only reason I'm here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "331||||4"
msgid "Why exactly did you feel it\r\nnecessary to kill him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "332||||4"
msgid "What did he do to betray the Saio?"
msgstr ""

